---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="Why STR Manuals exists.">
  <section class="container-page py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-6">About</p>
      <h1 class="mb-10">A different shape of host education.</h1>

      <div class="measure space-y-5 text-lg">
        <p>
          STR Manuals is part of an ecosystem of tools built for short-term rental
          operators — alongside The STR Ledger (Excel workbooks), strhost.tools (free
          calculators), and a handful of audience-specific sites.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most STR education is shaped wrong. It's a 4-hour video that buries the
          answer. A $2,000 coaching program. A forum thread with 87 conflicting replies.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each manual here picks one question, answers it in plain English, and gives
          you the templates and checklists to act on it tomorrow. The format is
          intentionally short — 25 to 50 pages — because long manuals don't get read.
        </p>
        <p>
          They're written for the operator who'd rather pay $25 and have an answer
          tonight than spend three weekends on YouTube.
        </p>

        <hr class="rule" />

        <p class="eyebrow">Operating principles</p>

        <ul class="space-y-4 text-base list-none pl-0">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600;">01</span>
            <span><strong>One problem per manual.</strong> No "complete guides." If a topic needs three manuals, it gets three.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600;">02</span>
            <span><strong>Plain English over jargon.</strong> If you need an MBA to read it, the manual failed.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600;">03</span>
            <span><strong>Templates included.</strong> Every manual ships with at least one fillable workbook or checklist.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600;">04</span>
            <span><strong>Free updates.</strong> Tax law and Airbnb rules change. Buyers get all updates within the same major version.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600;">05</span>
            <span><strong>14-day "didn't help" refund.</strong> No interrogation. Email, refund, done.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
